               <msContents>
                  <summary>Hymns known as Anqäṣ Zema, አንቀጽ፡ ዜማ፡, Prayer of the Covenant, ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡, Supplication, መስተብቁዕ, Various Litanies, ሊጦን፡, Office Prayers, መስተብቁዕ፡, Ziq Chants, መጽሐፈ፡ ዚቅ፡</summary>
